# Device Ignore List for HelixQA
# ================================
# Devices listed here will be excluded from HelixQA autonomous testing.
# Each line is a case-insensitive substring match against the device
# model name from `adb devices -l`.
#
# Examples:
#   ATMOSphere     — excludes all ATMOSphere (rk3588) devices
#   emulator       — excludes Android emulators
#   Pixel          — excludes Pixel phones
#
# Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.

ATMOSphere
